com.magnet.core.api

Interface PostStarted


  • @Contract
public interface PostStarted
    Called for kernel-managed services after the kernel enters the ServicesListener.Event#STARTED state.

    This is a simple alternative for being a full ServicesListener.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void postStarted()
      Called post construction, and post kernel startup.
